OL,3,CDrivers warned of three month road
OL,4,Cclosure ahead of A303 Stonehenge
OL,5,Cupgrade
OL,7,FMotorists are being warned that a
OL,8,Fsection of the A360 in Wiltshire is
OL,9,Fset to close for three months as work
OL,10,Fgets underway to prepare for the A303
OL,11,FStonehenge upgrade.
OL,13,FFollowing the recent High Court ruling
OL,14,Fin favour of the scheme, National
OL,15,FHighways is now firming up plans for
OL,16,Fthe essential utilities work,
OL,17,Fincluding suppling electricity for the
OL,18,Fconstruction and the tunnel in the
OL,19,Flong term.
