OL,5,Cupgrade
OL,7,FThe A360 will close from early next
OL,8,Fmonth, just after the Easter Bank
OL,9,FHoliday weekend, between the junction
OL,10,Fof The Avenue and Longbarrow junction
OL,11,Fon the A303.
OL,13,FHigh voltage and fibre optic cabling
OL,14,Fwill be installed along the route,
OL,15,Fwhich National Highways says requires
OL,16,Fa full closure for safety reasons, due
OL,17,Fto the narrow width of the road and
OL,18,Fminimal space along the verges.
