OL,7,FDuring the closure, traffic will be
OL,8,Fdiverted via the A345 and sections of
OL,9,Fthe A303 and A36, as per the diagram.
OL,11,FTo enable the underground cabling to
OL,12,Fbe completed before the school summer
OL,13,Fholidays, National Highways says the
OL,14,Fwork will be carried out seven days a
OL,15,Fweek, with some overnight working.
