OL,7,FProvision will be made for emergency
OL,8,Fservices access and access for local
OL,9,Flandowners, residents and businesses
OL,10,Faffected by the closures, and
OL,11,Farrangements will be discussed shortly
OL,12,Fwith residents alongside and close to
OL,13,Fthe A360.
