OL,4,Cclosure ahead of A303 Stonehenge
OL,5,Cupgrade
OL,7,FDavid Bullock, National Highways'
OL,8,FProject Director for the A303
OL,9,FStonehenge scheme, said, "The road
OL,10,Fscheme will ultimately tackle the
OL,11,Flongstanding issue of rat running and
OL,12,Fprovide a real benefit to local
OL,13,Fcommunities, and for this essential
OL,14,Fpreliminary work, we'll be doing all
OL,15,Fwe can to put in measures to lessen
OL,16,Fthe impact of this work."
OL,18,F"We need to carry out the work now to
OL,19,Fensure our programme timescales and we
OL,20,Fwant to give local communities as much
OL,21,Fnotice as possible."
