OL,5,Cupgrade
OL,7,F"We appreciate that roadworks and road
OL,8,Fclosures can be frustrating and we'd
OL,9,Flike to thank motorists, local
OL,10,Fresidents and businesses in advance
OL,11,Ffor their patience."
OL,13,F"We have deliberately avoided the
OL,14,Fsummer holiday season, but we
OL,15,Fappreciate the work will impact the
OL,16,FWhitsun Week traffic and the Summer
OL,17,FSolstice, and we'll be working hard to
OL,18,Fminimise disruption during those times
OL,19,Fand where we can."
