OL,7,FCllr Caroline Thomas, Wiltshire
OL,8,FCouncil Cabinet Member for Transport,
OL,9,Fsaid, "We know that this closure will
OL,10,Faffect many Wiltshire residents and
OL,11,Fvisitors, and so our officers have
OL,12,Fbeen working closely with partner
OL,13,Fagencies to ensure any disruption is
OL,14,Fkept to a minimum.
